summary:
With over 20 years of experience in the ICT sector Arjen has grown from being an engineer to project manager. With this experience and knowledge Arjen can quickly switch between different disciplines. This makes him an accessible conversationalist from server room to boardroom. This at an operational, tactical and strategic level.

Strong characteristics

•	Plan, coordinate;
•	Mutual relationships (team building);
•	Result-based scoping, time and budget.

Qualities and characteristics that are central

•	Analytical and pragmatic;
•	Initiative and responsibility;
•	Accessible and humorous;
•	Integrity and loyalty.
